children.name: SELECT "catalogue_productattribute"."code", "catalogue_productattribute"."type" FROM "catalogue_productattribute" WHERE "catalogue_productattribute"."code" IN ('hypothenusa') ORDER BY "catalogue_productattribute"."code" ASC

SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_product" INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattributevalue" ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = "catalogue_productattributevalue"."product_id") INNER JOIN "catalogue_productattribute" ON ("catalogue_productattributevalue"."attribute_id" = "catalogue_productattribute"."id") WHERE ("catalogue_productattributevalue"."value_float" = 1.25 AND "catalogue_productattribute"."code" = 'hypothenusa') LIMIT 1
